OL,3,CNorthern Ireland suffers second night
OL,4,Cof unrest as rioters attack police
OL,6,FA Department for Infrastructure
OL,7,Fvehicle was left in flames as rioters
OL,8,Fconfronted police near the Sandyknowes
OL,9,Froundabout in Newtownabbey to the
OL,10,Fnorth west of Belfast.
OL,12,FFootage showed dozens of men dressed
OL,13,Fall in black and wearing face
OL,14,Fcoverings gathering on Antrim Road,
OL,15,Fwhere they could be seen tearing
OL,16,Fbricks from properties and smashing
OL,17,Fpaving stones with sledgehammers to
OL,18,Fcreate projectiles to throw at police.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
