OL,3,CNorthern Ireland suffers second night
OL,4,Cof unrest as rioters attack police
OL,6,FHadi Alodid, 30, appeared in court on
OL,7,FWednesday, charged with attempted
OL,8,Fmurder over Monday's knife attack in
OL,9,Fwhich the victim, Stephen Ogilvie,
OL,10,Flost an eye.
OL,12,FMr Ogilvie, who is aged in his 40s, is
OL,13,Fin a stable condition in hospital in
OL,14,FBelfast, his family said.
OL,16,FMr Ogilvie's family urged people to
OL,17,Fstop sharing "false information on
OL,18,Fsocial media" about the attack, adding
OL,19,Fthat they were left "feeling
OL,20,Fdisgusted" by the recent disorder.
OL,26,@yD@NOUzD@MO]{D@UOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
