OL,3,CNorthern Ireland suffers second night
OL,4,Cof unrest as rioters attack police
OL,6,FIn a statement issued by police on
OL,7,FWednesday night, they said: "We want
OL,8,Fto make it absolutely clear that to do
OL,9,Fthis in response is not supported by
OL,10,Four family, and peaceful protest is
OL,11,Fonly ever the way forward.
OL,13,F"We have many migrants who make a
OL,14,Fdeeply valuable contribution to our
OL,15,Fcountry, including from within our
OL,16,Fhealthcare system and hospitality
OL,17,Fsector, and we depend on them to make
OL,18,Four country work.
OL,26,@oD@]OUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
