OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1781312588
OL,3,CNorthern Ireland suffers second night
OL,4,Cof unrest as rioters attack police
OL,6,F"We do not want this terrible tragedy
OL,7,Fto be used to divide people or fuel
OL,8,Fhostility ` do not do this in the name
OL,9,Fof our loved one as we do not share
OL,10,Fthe same values."
OL,12,FThe reaction to the incident saw mobs
OL,13,Fset homes, a bus and cars on fire in
OL,14,FBelfast on Tuesday, with people
OL,15,Ftargeted based on their race.
OL,17,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer vowed
OL,18,Fto "crack down on anyone who is
OL,19,Ffuelling this division".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@QO]zD@DOU{D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
